                " Universite Laval"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "13C+ 13C++ 11B+ 11B++ and 10B+ beams"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two NaI detectors, 12.7 cm diameter x 10.2 cm",
                " thick, placed on either side of the target chamber,",
                " consisting of a cross made from stainless steel tubing",
                " of 1.59 cm external diameter and 0.254 mm wall",
                " thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Targets of thicknesses varying between 30 and 150",
                " microg/cm2. The 13C targets (enriched to 99.7 %) were",
                " commercially purchased. The boron targets were",
                " fabricated by evaporating 10B and 11B isotopes",
                " (both enriched to 98.5 %) onto BaCl coated glass",
                " slides for the self-supporting targets and onto glass",
                " slides with 10 microg/cm2 thick carbon foil for the",
                " carbon-backed targets."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "PART-DET": [
            {
